move of God coming to

00:20:19.630 --> 00:20:19.640
Hollywood—to

00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:24.390
A-list

00:20:24.400 --> 00:20:26.830
celebrities like Justin

00:20:26.830 --> 00:20:26.840
Bieber. They

00:20:26.840 --> 00:20:29.230
are

00:20:47.159 --> 00:20:49.390
hurting

00:20:49.390 --> 00:20:49.400
and

00:20:49.400 --> 00:20:51.549
thirsty

00:20:51.549 --> 00:20:51.559
for

00:20:51.559 --> 00:20:53.909
more. They

00:20:56.390 --> 00:20:56.400
will

00:20:59.960 --> 00:21:01.870
have

00:21:01.870 --> 00:21:01.880
a

00:21:01.880 --> 00:21:03.789
great influence in bringing others to

00:21:03.799 --> 00:21:06.710
the kingdom because God

00:21:16.110 --> 00:21:16.120
will

00:21:25.320 --> 00:21:26.430
touch even the

00:21:26.440 --> 00:21:29.590
hardest people.

00:21:35.440 --> 00:21:39.029
I want to read

00:21:39.029 --> 00:21:39.039
a

00:21:39.039 --> 00:21:42.350
beautiful testimony about a healing that

00:21:42.360 --> 00:21:44.990
took place at Azusa Street.

00:21:56.840 --> 00:21:58.269
The Lord told me He wants

00:21:58.269 --> 00:21:58.279
His

00:21:58.279 --> 00:22:02.669
people to believe bigger.

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:18.110
This

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:32.710
story

00:22:32.710 --> 00:22:32.720
is

00:22:32.720 --> 00:22:34.950
of a child whose second

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:37.390
teeth grew in rotten and black.

00:22:39.760 --> 00:22:42.590
Lucille said, 'God will heal

00:22:42.600 --> 00:22:44.990
anything.'Lucille

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:46.750
laid

00:22:46.760 --> 00:22:48.909
a handkerchief

00:22:50.720 --> 00:22:53.190
over the child's mouth and prayed.

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:55.110
A handful of blackened teeth

00:22:55.120 --> 00:22:56.950
dropped into

00:22:56.950 --> 00:22:56.960
a

00:22:56.960 --> 00:23:00.830
cup.

00:23:05.470 --> 00:23:05.480
Then

00:23:10.279 --> 00:23:13.070
new

00:23:19.320 --> 00:23:22.630
teeth grew in one at a time.

00:23:31.440 --> 00:23:34.149
The child

00:23:37.159 --> 00:23:39.390
said it kind of

00:23:39.400 --> 00:23:42.549
tickled.

00:23:58.679 --> 00:24:00.430
Sister Lucille was a

00:24:00.430 --> 00:24:00.440
little

00:24:00.440 --> 00:24:02.510
woman,

00:24:02.510 --> 00:24:02.520
but

00:24:02.520 --> 00:24:04.470
she

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:06.230
could command

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:08.110
a leg to grow or

00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:08.120
a

00:24:08.120 --> 00:24:10.710
wrist

00:24:10.720 --> 00:24:12.750
to

00:24:12.760 --> 00:24:14.510
heal.

00:24:14.520 --> 00:24:16.710
She

00:24:18.470 --> 00:24:18.480
described

00:24:23.510 --> 00:24:23.520
the

00:24:26.600 --> 00:24:28.990
Shekinah

00:24:30.919 --> 00:24:33.350
Glory

00:24:33.360 --> 00:24:35.950
as

00:24:35.950 --> 00:24:35.960
a

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:38.389
mist-like

00:24:38.399 --> 00:24:41.230
cloud.

00:24:41.240 --> 00:24:43.470
She would sit

00:25:15.360 --> 00:25:17.430
in it and play in it,

00:25:22.590 --> 00:25:22.600
and

00:25:27.240 --> 00:25:29.669
it was like breathing in pure oxygen.

00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:34.870
The scent was like lilacs

00:25:34.870 --> 00:25:34.880
or

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:37.909
roses.

00:25:40.000 --> 00:25:42.950
When

00:25:42.960 --> 00:25:44.909
they would

00:25:44.919 --> 00:25:46.870
sing in the Spirit,

00:25:46.870 --> 00:25:46.880
the

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:48.710
glory would

00:25:48.720 --> 00:25:51.190
rise and fill the whole room.

00:26:25.120 --> 00:26:28.549
Megan is going to be radically healed like

00:26:28.549 --> 00:26:28.559
that.

00:26:28.559 --> 00:26:31.549
I'm expecting it.

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:42.029
It will be a

00:26:42.039 --> 00:26:45.310
sign to the world that Jesus Christ is

00:26:45.320 --> 00:26:48.630
the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:26:58.399 --> 00:27:01.950
I'm trying to inspire you to

00:27:01.960 --> 00:27:05.510
believe bigger.

00:27:05.520 --> 00:27:07.389
This is

00:27:07.399 --> 00:27:10.149
how I keep myself

00:27:10.159 --> 00:27:12.149
afloat—testimonies

00:27:14.549 --> 00:27:14.559
and

00:27:17.360 --> 00:27:19.190
Kenneth

00:27:21.510 --> 00:27:21.520
Hagin's

00:27:22.960 --> 00:27:26.029
books.

00:27:37.880 --> 00:27:39.750
Faith

00:27:39.750 --> 00:27:39.760
comes

00:27:39.760 --> 00:27:41.029
by hearing.

00:28:06.679 --> 00:28:09.509
We have

00:28:09.519 --> 00:28:12.389
challenges,

00:28:12.399 --> 00:28:14.430
but

00:28:14.440 --> 00:28:17.110
God is faithful.

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:22.149
We live by faith,

00:28:22.159 --> 00:28:23.950
selling

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:25.870
on eBay and

00:28:25.880 --> 00:28:28.830
Poshmark.

00:28:33.799 --> 00:28:35.750
Here

00:28:37.880 --> 00:28:40.110
is a testimony from a brother who had

00:28:40.120 --> 00:28:43.590
a visitation from Jesus.

00:28:43.600 --> 00:28:47.669
He

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:33.549
was praying

00:29:33.559 --> 00:29:35.669
at his kitchen table

00:29:35.669 --> 00:29:35.679
and

00:29:35.679 --> 00:29:38.549
saw

00:29:38.559 --> 00:29:41.149
a

00:29:41.149 --> 00:29:41.159
vision

00:29:41.159 --> 00:29:43.750
of

00:29:43.760 --> 00:29:46.549
himself

00:29:46.549 --> 00:29:46.559
in

00:29:46.559 --> 00:29:50.350
a

00:29:50.360 --> 00:29:53.470
field.

00:30:16.159 --> 00:30:18.870
The Lord walked

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:20.750
up

00:30:20.760 --> 00:30:23.149
and said, 'Come on, get up; it's time

00:30:23.159 --> 00:30:26.669
to

00:30:29.870 --> 00:30:29.880
work.'He

00:30:32.440 --> 00:30:35.509
wore

00:30:37.760 --> 00:30:41.350
simple white robes

00:30:41.350 --> 00:30:41.360
and

00:30:41.360 --> 00:30:43.870
had

00:30:43.880 --> 00:30:47.830
dark skin, long

00:30:47.840 --> 00:30:50.269
hair, and a dark beard.

00:30:50.279 --> 00:30:52.310
They

00:30:52.320 --> 00:30:54.669
walked

00:30:54.679 --> 00:30:57.029
through

00:30:57.039 --> 00:30:59.870
hills

00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:02.669
of

00:31:02.679 --> 00:31:04.669
cattle,

00:31:04.679 --> 00:31:07.990
and

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:10.590
the

00:31:10.600 --> 00:31:12.909
Lord

00:31:12.919 --> 00:31:15.269
said, 'I

00:31:24.080 --> 00:31:26.830
need

00:31:26.840 --> 00:31:29.509
a

00:31:29.519 --> 00:31:31.710
cowboy.'The

00:31:31.720 --> 00:31:35.230
brother

00:31:35.240 --> 00:31:38.389
said, 'You've got one, Lord.'The Lord

00:31:40.600 --> 00:31:43.470
said, 'A

00:31:43.480 --> 00:31:46.830
cowboy needs a horse,'and

00:31:46.830 --> 00:31:46.840
the brother

00:31:46.840 --> 00:31:49.590
replied, 'Even a string

00:31:49.600 --> 00:31:52.470
of horses, Lord.'It made Him smile.

00:32:59.320 --> 00:33:04.110
Jesus

00:33:04.120 --> 00:33:08.830
communicates as a

00:33:08.840 --> 00:33:11.389
friend.

00:34:04.240 --> 00:34:07.629
If you don't know Him,

00:34:07.629 --> 00:34:07.639
this

00:34:07.639 --> 00:34:10.310
is

00:34:10.320 --> 00:34:14.550
your

00:34:16.599 --> 00:34:20.750
last call. Will you

00:34:20.760 --> 00:34:24.750
bow your knee today?

00:35:16.670 --> 00:35:16.680
No

00:36:10.319 --> 00:36:12.470
sin

00:36:12.470 --> 00:36:12.480
is

00:36:12.480 --> 00:36:15.870
too big for Jesus to forgive.

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:24.470
Say this prayer:

00:36:26.319 --> 00:36:28.950
'Jesus, I'm a

00:36:28.960 --> 00:36:31.790
sinner. Write my name in the Lamb's Book

00:36:31.800 --> 00:36:34.109
of Life. I

00:36:34.119 --> 00:36:37.870
believe You are the Son of God.

00:36:37.880 --> 00:36:40.470
Forgive me of my sins.

00:36:40.480 --> 00:36:43.069
I want

00:36:43.079 --> 00:36:46.510
to come home. Thank You

00:36:46.510 --> 00:36:46.520
for

00:36:46.520 --> 00:36:48.790
setting

00:36:48.800 --> 00:36:50.470
me free from sin,

00:36:50.480 --> 00:36:52.870
sickness, and

00:37:00.030 --> 00:37:00.040
disease.'Now,

00:37:09.040 --> 00:37:12.230
find

00:37:12.230 --> 00:37:12.240
a

00:37:12.240 --> 00:37:15.109
Bible

00:37:15.119 --> 00:37:16.630
and

00:37:16.640 --> 00:37:18.990
a

00:37:19.000 --> 00:37:20.630
good

00:37:20.640 --> 00:37:23.510
church.

00:37:49.319 --> 00:37:51.870
Let's

00:37:51.880 --> 00:37:54.710
believe for your miracle now.

00:37:54.710 --> 00:37:54.720
Father,

00:37:54.720 --> 00:37:57.190
in

00:37:57.190 --> 00:37:57.200
the

00:37:57.200 --> 00:38:01.910
name

00:38:01.910 --> 00:38:01.920
of

00:38:01.920 --> 00:38:05.790
Jesus, I believe

00:38:05.790 --> 00:38:05.800
they are

00:38:05.800 --> 00:38:08.870
healed

00:39:25.359 --> 00:39:27.670
from the top of their head

00:39:27.680 --> 00:39:29.870
to the soles of their feet.

00:39:58.880 --> 00:40:04.390
Cancer, go now. Diabetes, go

00:40:04.400 --> 00:40:07.230
now. We call for new organs, restored eyesight, and hearing. I call

00:40:07.230 --> 00:40:07.240
for healing from strokes. We command tumors

00:40:07.240 --> 00:40:10.430
to shrivel and go. I thank You

00:40:10.430 --> 00:40:10.440
for restoration in the colon, stomach, and

00:40:10.440 --> 00:40:13.710
thyroid. I call for healing of the

00:40:13.710 --> 00:40:13.720
prostate, ovaries, and uterus. No more miscarriages.

00:40:13.720 --> 00:40:16.790
We

00:40:16.800 --> 00:40:19.630
call

00:43:13.280 --> 00:43:16.670
the

00:43:16.680 --> 00:43:19.630
wayward children home.

00:43:41.160 --> 00:43:43.510
I curse breast cancer;

00:43:43.520 --> 00:43:47.510
go now in Jesus'name. I call

00:43:47.510 --> 00:43:47.520
for

00:43:47.520 --> 00:43:49.589
healing

00:43:57.790 --> 00:43:57.800
of

00:44:06.520 --> 00:44:09.710
throat

00:44:16.280 --> 00:44:18.870
cancers and

00:44:21.240 --> 00:44:23.710
gum

00:44:23.720 --> 00:44:27.589
disease.

00:44:29.069 --> 00:44:29.079
I

00:44:31.680 --> 00:44:36.910
command

00:44:39.440 --> 00:44:42.829
Celiac disease

00:44:42.829 --> 00:44:42.839
to

00:44:42.839 --> 00:44:46.710
be

00:44:46.720 --> 00:44:49.750
healed.

00:45:00.119 --> 00:45:02.349
I thank You

00:45:02.349 --> 00:45:02.359
for

00:45:02.359 --> 00:45:04.109
restoring

00:45:04.119 --> 00:45:06.470
marriages.

00:45:19.960 --> 00:45:22.230
We believe for

00:45:22.240 --> 00:45:25.950
financial

00:45:25.950 --> 00:45:25.960
breakthroughs

00:45:25.960 --> 00:45:29.109
and

00:45:29.119 --> 00:45:32.109
creative ideas.

00:45:32.109 --> 00:45:32.119
Thank

00:45:32.119 --> 00:45:34.470
You,

00:45:34.480 --> 00:45:37.030
Father.

00:45:43.680 --> 00:45:46.549
Amen.

